## Environment Variables

Copy `.env.example` to `.env.local` and configure:

```bash
cp .env.example .env.local
```

{{#if (eq type "shell")}}
### Required Variables

- `VITE_AWS_USER_POOL_ID` - AWS Cognito User Pool ID
- `VITE_AWS_USER_POOL_WEB_CLIENT_ID` - AWS Cognito Client ID
- `VITE_SERVERLESS_API_BASE_URL` - Serverless API base URL

{{else if (eq type "module")}}
### Module Configuration

- `VITE_MODULE_NAME` - Module identifier
- `VITE_SHELL_APP_URL` - Shell application URL for development

